info.name: GBAtemp V4 Dark
info.description: Dark version of the new, post-hack GBAtemp V4.
info.additionalInfo:
4.3.1
Actually there's an official Dark Theme now but I like some stuff of this one better so I'll keep updating it to be used in conjunction with the official one. If you use this you might want to turn on the official Dark Theme as well.
-Some extra optimize stuff and one accidentally removed thing added back
-Fixed Access Control Panel being fugly
